sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>MitreHeatmapPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>MitreHeatmapView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>MitreTechniqueDetailView
    participant SER as MitreTechniqueSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Navigate to MITRE ATT&CK page
    FE->>API1: GET /api/mitre/heatmap/
    API1->>DB: MitreTactic.objects.prefetch_related("techniques")
    API1->>DB: Alert.objects.values("mitre_technique").annotate(Count)
    DB-->>API1: Tactics with technique alert counts
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK {tactics: [{name, techniques: [{id, name, count}]}]}
    FE->>FE: intensityColor(count) for each cell
    FE->>FE: Legend() component
    FE-->>U: Render ATT&CK heatmap matrix
    U->>FE: Click technique cell
    FE->>API2: GET /api/mitre/techniques/{technique_id}/
    API2->>DB: MitreTechnique.objects.get(pk=id)
    API2->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(mitre_technique=id)[:5]
    DB-->>API2: Technique + recent alerts
    API2->>SER: MitreTechniqueSerializer(technique)
    API2-->>FE: 200 OK {technique detail + recent alerts}
    FE->>FE: TechniqueDetailPanel(data)
    FE-->>U: Display technique details and related alerts
